data.description: Cute brick 3 bed 2 bath home, perfect for a first-time homebuyer or a great starter home. This home had a metal roof put on less than 5 years ago and has beautiful hardwood floor throughout. The backyard is fenced in and has a big, covered patio slab that would be perfect for BBQ's. This home has a ton of potential- it won't last long.
